description: The Lowepro The PixelPak V1 blends protection, style  and versatility into this compact case. Created with a rugged mixture of rubber, aluminum  and plastic, this card holder keeps your memory cards safe  and organized in a compact area.  The PixelPak V1 will hold up to eight (8) SD/MMC, XD or Mini SD memory cards, or you can replace the interchangeable insert to accommodate four (4) memory cards  and one (1) PCMCIA card.
title: Lowepro PixelPak V1 Accessory Case (Silver)
